tics-medspa-memorial-west?to=place.ChIJY814oJLbQIYR6n0sxVXo_x4"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.bcrnaesthetics.com/services/"},{"type":"url","url":"https://maps.apple.com/place?place-id=I8C646FC652B47B00"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.instagram.com/bcrnaesthetics/reel/DOed5zYkpmC/?hl=hu"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.instagram.com/bricollinsnp/"}]}},{"id":"ws_76f1793a-5771-9e90-93be-13c69548f972_call-f6002b47-d887-4301-a0a3-fe672c3008a2-6","type":"web_search_call","status":"completed","action":{"type":"search","query":"Clariti MedSpa Houston Aquagold address","sources":[{"type":"url","url":"https://www.yelp.com/biz/clariti-aesthetics-and-wellness-houston"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.facebook.com/claritiaesthetics/"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.claritimedspa.com/contact"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.claritimedspa.com/"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.mapquest.com/us/texas/clariti-aesthetics-wellness-456669359"},{"type":"url","url":"https://classpass.com/studios/clariti-aesthetics-and-wellness-houston"},{"type":"url","url":"https://aquagoldfinetouch.com/pages/locations"},{"type":"url","url":"https://prospeo.io/c/clariti-aesthetics-wellness"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.instagram.com/claritiaesthetics/"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.claritimedspa.com/all-services"}]}},{"id":"tco_76f1793a-5771-9e90-93be-13c69548f972_call-f6002b47-d887-4301-a0a3-fe672c3008a2-3","summary":[],"type":"reasoning","status":"completed"},{"id":"tco_76f1793a-5771-9e90-93be-13c69548f972_call-f6002b47-d887-4301-a0a3-fe672c3008a2-4","summary":[],"type":"reasoning","status":"completed"},{"id":"tco_76f1793a-5771-9e90-93be-13c69548f972_call-f6002b47-d887-4301-a0a3-fe672c3008a2-5","summary":[],"type":"reasoning","status":"completed"},{"id":"tco_76f1793a-5771-9e90-93be-13c69548f972_call-f6002b47-d887-4301-a0a3-fe672c3008a2-6","summary":[],"type":"reasoning","status":"completed"},{"content":[{"type":"output_text","text":"**Several medspas, aesthetics clinics, and plastic surgery practices in Houston and nearby suburbs (such as The Woodlands and Spring) offer Aquagold (also called AquaGold or AQUAGOLD Fine Touch) facial treatments.**[[1]](https://houstonskinhealth.com/aquagold-facial/)[[2]](https://drsharonaesthetics.com/aquagold-microneedling-houston-texas/)\n\nAquagold is a microinfusion/microneedling treatment using fine 24K gold-plated needles to deliver customized serums (often including Botox, hyaluronic acid, peptides, vitamins, or other ingredients) into the skin for improved glow, reduced pores/fine lines/wrinkles, hydration, and collagen stimulation, typically with minimal downtime.[[2]](https://drsharonaesthetics.com/aquagold-microneedling-houston-texas/)\n\nHere are some providers in or near Houston based on current web information (verify details, availability, and pricing directly, as they can change):\n\n- **Dr. Sharon Aesthetics** (Houston) — 1014 Wirt Road, Bldg 290, Suite 118, Houston, TX 77055. Phone: 832-270-9241. Offers Aquagold microneedling for glow in ~20 minutes; customizable with Botox, HA, etc. Hours: Mon–Fri 9am–5pm, Sat 10am–4pm. Website: drsharonaesthetics.com.[[2]](https://drsharonaesthetics.com/aquagold-microneedling-houston-texas/)\n\n- **BCRN Aesthetics** (Houston, serving Heights, Rice Military, and nearby) — 6001 Washington Ave #500, Houston, TX 77007. Phone: (346) 200-8520 or (713) 806-4742. Email: info@bcrnaesthetics.com. Provides microchanneling Aquagold facials. Website: bcrnaesthetics.com.[[3]](https://www.bcrnaesthetics.com/services/microchanneling-aquagold-facial/)\n\n- **Nia Aesthetics** (Houston, Montrose area) — 4203 Montrose Blvd #440, Houston, TX 77006. Phones: (210) 864-1599 or (210) 595-9324. Custom Aquagold treatments by Dr. Nia, focused on glow, hydration, and texture. Website: niaaestheticsmd.com.[[4]](https://niaaestheticsmd.com/services/facials/aqua-gold/)\n\n- **Clariti Aesthetics & Wellness** (Houston and Sealy) — 12512 Memorial Dr., Ste A, Houston, TX 77024. Phone: (713) 324-8889 or (832) 726-1590. Offers AquaGold facials. Website: claritimedspa.com.[[5]](https://www.yelp.com/biz/clariti-aesthetics-and-wellness-houston)\n\n- **Other notable options**:\n  - Lind Plastic Surgery (Houston & The Woodlands).\n  - Texas Face by Eugene Alford, MD (Houston area).\n  - Belage Center, Queen Aesthetics, Houston Skin Health, Beauty Becomes You, Skin Lab Houston/Woodlands, and Galleria Aesthetics (various Houston locations).[[3]](https://www.bcrnaesthetics.com/services/microchanneling-aquagold-facial/)\n\n**Recommendations**: Search RealSelf or similar directories for patient reviews and provider ratings. Schedule a consultation to discuss your skin goals, as treatments are often customized. Prices typically range from several hundred dollars per session (packages may be available). Confirm they use authentic AQUAGOLD devices and check for any current promotions or requirements (e.g., avoiding certain skincare beforehand).[[4]](https://niaaestheticsmd.com/services/facials/aqua-gold/)\n\nFor the most up-to-date listings, try a local search like “Aquagold Houston” or contact the providers directly. If you have a specific area of Houston (e.g., Heights, Memorial, or The Woodlands) or preferences, I can help refine this further!","logprobs":[],"annotations":[{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://houstonskinhealth.com/aquagold-facial/","start_index":215,"end_index":268,"title":"1"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://drsharonaesthetics.com/aquagold-microneedling-houston-texas/","start_index":268,"end_index":343,"title":"2"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://drsharonaesthetics.com/aquagold-microneedling-houston-texas/","start_index":681,"end_index":756,"title":"2"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://drsharonaesthetics.com/aquagold-microneedling-houston-texas/","start_index":1185,"end_index":1260,"title":"2"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.bcrnaesthetics.com/services/microchanneling-aquagold-facial/","start_index":1529,"end_index":16